{"tid":516874,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[感謝主]附近間M記終於肯換新收銀系統","createTime":"2018-01-01T18:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T10:36:13.000Z","uid":75735,"like":277,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1013f1d3ce429a3b91322897acb8bb26b8dc6b34","tid":516874,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/023319_2547d5995c2113e3c96656724dbdd54e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F023319_2547d5995c2113e3c96656724dbdd54e.jpeg&h=90feb411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>垃撚圾</strong></span></span><br />\n以為分工合作就會有效率?<br />\n成個idea根本就戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前排隊落完order兩三分鐘就可以拎番屋企食<br />\n而家落親M記買外賣15分鐘有已經算快<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲未計由屋內企來回既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後放兩部自助收銀機<br />\n就以為可以代替人手 開少兩條收銀員線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根本冇人識用</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD死廢老C奶禁極都唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又想懶醒學用新野<br />\n仲要係部機面前圍威喂討論要加d咩野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似前世未見過menu咁<br />\n唔識用就死番去排收銀員條隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你以為你係到行街買衫呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面成村人等緊你呀仆街 阻撚住曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪撚見到條隊得3條友就走去排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上仲慢過排緊10個人既人手收銀員<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於落到單你以好快有得拎外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係稔多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n排隊拎野食果邊又係塞滿一大堆人<br />\n睇曬成條youtube片<br />\n個number仲係有撚排都未輪到我<br />\n知唔知乜撚野叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快餐</span></span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次落完order要係附近兜個圈番黎再等拎外賣<br />\n我唔撚叫譚仔茶記?<br />\n點解要食你d垃圾食物呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">M記我屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"6dd3ed1b3b1143094813680d2cdcda72104254c1","tid":516874,"uid":150618,"like":146,"dislike":8,"score":138,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:11:58.000Z","msg":"又要屌又要繼續幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8e8516ae3eb735228277bfa398066658157064","tid":516874,"uid":44068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:35:05.000Z","msg":"我樓下個間仲未換<br />\n成日排成4～5條隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好在我買野個陣好少人買完個員工轉個身就到我手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2ce6a34f6cfc572aab8903e6778ca3e7c42462","tid":516874,"uid":19947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:37:07.000Z","msg":"最撚慘部機成撚日壞機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba97652a13672f9b0b5c027bdeddb5afed6d788","tid":516874,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:38:00.000Z","msg":"咩收銀系統"},{"pid":"b960e2eedb35f1f8c8d7be59cf99d8511378abf7","tid":516874,"uid":96,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:40:55.000Z","msg":"自助收銀機幾好啊 成班阿嬸廢中唔識用又要係部機前面妹下妹下<br />\n多謝佢地先冇人排收銀個邊 我去收銀個邊俾完錢拎埋餐班on9仲係部機前面妹下妹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026a9cf7f2ba9806ca81993c4b77592b7f47e91f","tid":516874,"uid":39177,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:43:20.000Z","msg":"樂富果間,任何時段冇15-20分鐘都唔會有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f9635a382301a4bc21e1f9cb1ac313fc501b3d","tid":516874,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樂富果間,任何時段冇15-20分鐘都唔會有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger............"},{"pid":"4359f80a1ccec46d1e9e9b92a64f88a4f2f78f64","tid":516874,"uid":147367,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:55:59.000Z","msg":"佢最on9唔係個收錢系統<br />\n佢廚房既分工先最on9，完全無以前既彈性<br />\n以前多人既佢會叫多個人入去整包，飲品同薯條呢啲邊個得閒邊個搞<br />\n依家每個人都只可以負責一樣野<br />\n試過飲品同拎包果個得閒到吹水，因為出餐果度積左十幾個餐出唔切，但完全無人諗過去幫手出餐<br />\n結果我個餐由執完再到我手用左五分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba52ebf5ffabf680105857ea4b2c89b79d000b87","tid":516874,"uid":54404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4359f80a1ccec46d1e9e9b92a64f88a4f2f78f64","tid":516874,"uid":147367,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:55:59.000Z","msg":"佢最on9唔係個收錢系統<br />\n佢廚房既分工先最on9，完全無以前既彈性<br />\n以前多人既佢會叫多個人入去整包，飲品同薯條呢啲邊個得閒邊個搞<br />\n依家每個人都只可以負責一樣野<br />\n試過飲品同拎包果個得閒到吹水，因為出餐果度積左十幾個餐出唔切，但完全無人諗過去幫手出餐<br />\n結果我個餐由執完再到我手用左五分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T22:50:39.000Z","msg":"出餐唔係個個識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有問題只係請唔夠人"},{"pid":"5e791f13f305cd5439fdbed5d0b02c0e489c7222","tid":516874,"uid":15984,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T22:57:39.000Z","msg":"以前既感覺係快啲<br />\n不過其實排隊耐左"},{"pid":"3063214c585a6b0a2ee7eabafe0e626e8479abfd","tid":516874,"uid":15984,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:08:07.000Z","msg":"而家係排隊時間少左<br />\n比錢過程快左<br />\n不過等野食既過程慢左"},{"pid":"f45161b13af2cb1754eab9b25abec04433d30f28","tid":516874,"uid":33424,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:10:19.000Z","msg":"用完自助收銀機, 係counter通常等成分鐘先有人黎收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bed50323c7d9eab8899e46922ef408ab29639e","tid":516874,"uid":2059,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:11:37.000Z","msg":"M記話錢已袋 理撚得你 慢慢等啦！"},{"pid":"835792963b2f3cc729c50533cfd25911354ac839","tid":516874,"uid":33868,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:12:50.000Z","msg":"佢部落餐機真係好撚慢好撚慢呀，可唔可以disable transition effect，都唔知有咩用"},{"pid":"1072c46f225860807ad33e0bb3950ccba8916aef","tid":516874,"uid":15984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:13:28.000Z","msg":"而家最好既做法就係買完野食，去個廁所再洗手<br />\n番到黎差唔多<br />\n<br />\n以前就直落排隊買野拎野無得行開"},{"pid":"dc42e684c03571dcc7cfe6e908e05a01d07d10b0","tid":516874,"uid":32570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:21:50.000Z","msg":"元朗？"},{"pid":"25dec75be7f9669bb9b8e1154f16228235772f1f","tid":516874,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:00:52.000Z","msg":"咪撚再食m 記喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c42b53ce8edb9f73d9d118b7ee17d9abdcec8b6","tid":516874,"uid":24641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:44:03.000Z","msg":"上個月方加個時去銅鑼灣個間食<br />\n屌鳩佢一上到去心諗咩事咁多人呀<br />\n落完等左成大半個鐘先有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢有4部定5部啲自助落單機 又開counter<br />\n入面又做唔切但係又接咁多單<br />\n搞到成堆人比左錢係度戇鳩等"},{"pid":"d38e9efac7247fe967e7f5f58e95adb4ccd94a4b","tid":516874,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"其實麥當勞係餐廳<br />\n唔係快餐店"},{"pid":"0d5fba027307dfb7fecec8561536d6427a650612","tid":516874,"uid":33376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"On9得過唔識用部自助機，當正係Menu不停禁，禁完去counter買，來來去去都係果幾餐架啦，最多咪係多左果期promotion果兩三個飽架啦<br />\n<br />\n攞餐又越黎越慢，執餐果個又要沖埋野飲，越黎越慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc15955557dff37f9c8c35759f8dca2d52727d80","tid":516874,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:11:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95613a8d393e7e2c1bbf4585def358464aff481d","tid":516874,"uid":38030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:19:41.000Z","msg":"九龍地城廣場三部機有兩部長期壞，一部唔夠用結果又死死氣開返counter。個送餐系統又係形同虛設，長期因為唔夠人手而唔放牌，屌你裝修咁撚大輪最尾都係排返counter<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5498c23fc3c238e20260c813c9be366e98937b","tid":516874,"uid":75735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"仲有泰式辣醬唔講係唔會比<br />\n垃撚圾"},{"pid":"d56877536189e689824815b8d17b4dbd8eb80ff9","tid":516874,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"當人傻仔，錢就收咗先，人就要焗等，慢以前好多，之後到以家都冇食過老麥。"},{"pid":"0c1df12fa02f986489942ce701a0a4ddc2026869","tid":516874,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761ae9c53af28613eda2ac369145531205566223","tid":516874,"uid":113002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d38e